This is my first CSS map, so it isn't the best.

It turned out pretty well. 

If you can't see the textures please tell me. I will try to fix that as soon as someone says anything.

It is a very stable map, no known bugs, and was tested for a long while. 

I made all the textures myself, besides the glass.
